data.description: Welcome home to your 3 Bed 2.5 Bath stunner in Picket Fences! This home is perfect for the family, and dog as well! Walk in to a gorgeous modern home, featuring a nook under the stairs for the pets & a custom doggy gate at the stairs! The Kitchen features granite countertops/ SS appliances! There is powder room off of the living room and a small mud room area at the front door! Upstairs you will find a nice loft / flex space and all three bedrooms + laundry. The primary suite is equipped with a large master bath/huge walk in closet! Laundry is right by the primary for convenience! SELLER OFFERING CLOSING COSTS OR 2-1 RATE BUY DOWN.
